(58, 0, '超6省份将上调公务员工资', '叔叔', NULL, '&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 0.85em; line-height: 1.8em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;著作权归作者所有。&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;商业转载请联系作者获得授权，非商业转载请注明出处。&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;作者：火晴云&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;链接：https://www.zhihu.com/question/19621333/answer/14509610&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;来源：知乎&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 0.85em; line-height: 1.8em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;似乎大多数回答是一年前的了 &amp;nbsp;更新一下这里的一些争议吧&amp;nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;JQuery从1.7版本开始将bind(),live()和delegate()方法合并成了on()方法了&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;同样unbind(),die()和undelegate()方法也合并成了off()方法&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;新旧API对比:&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;$(&amp;#39;a&amp;#39;).bind(&amp;#39;click&amp;#39;, myHandler);&amp;nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;$(&amp;#39;a&amp;#39;).on(&amp;#39;click&amp;#39;, myHandler);&amp;nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;$(&amp;#39;form&amp;#39;).bind(&amp;#39;submit&amp;#39;, { val: 42 }, fn);&amp;nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;$(&amp;#39;form&amp;#39;).on(&amp;#39;submit&amp;#39;, { val: 42 }, fn);&amp;nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;$(window).unbind(&amp;#39;scroll.myPlugin&amp;#39;);&amp;nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;$(window).off(&amp;#39;scroll.myPlugin&amp;#39;);&amp;nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;$(&amp;#39;.comment&amp;#39;).delegate(&amp;#39;a.add&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;click&amp;#39;, addNew);&amp;nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;$(&amp;#39;.comment&amp;#39;).on(&amp;#39;click&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;a.add&amp;#39;, addNew);&amp;nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;$(&amp;#39;.dialog&amp;#39;).undelegate(&amp;#39;a&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;click.myDlg&amp;#39;);&amp;nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;$(&amp;#39;.dialog&amp;#39;).off(&amp;#39;click.myDlg&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;a&amp;#39;); &amp;nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;$(&amp;#39;a&amp;#39;).live(&amp;#39;click&amp;#39;, fn);&amp;nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;$(document).on(&amp;#39;click&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;a&amp;#39;, fn);&amp;nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;$(&amp;#39;a&amp;#39;).die(&amp;#39;click&amp;#39;);&amp;nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;$(document).off(&amp;#39;click&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;a&amp;#39;);&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;了解更多:&lt;a href=&quot;http://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//blog.jquery.com/2011/11/03/jquery-1-7-released/&quot; class=&quot; external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.5s; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; visibility: hidden;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;visible&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;blog.jquery.com/2011/11&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;'),
(59, 0, '32444444', '232323', NULL, '&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;最高法回应“开放小区”是否与物权法相违背&quot; src=&quot;http://img1.gtimg.com/news/pics/hv1/143/64/2024/131627063.jpg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:center;FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;FONT-SIZE: 14px&quot;&gt;资料图。图片来源：视觉中国 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;rv-js-autoplay enabled&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot; bosszone=&quot;bofang_button_close&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;自动播放开关&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;自动播放&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;rv-title&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://v.qq.com/page/f/v/g/f0019il56vg.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;律师：开放小区与物权法不冲突 征收方案有待商榷&lt;/a&gt;\r\n\r\n &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://mat1.gtimg.com/news/dc/images/16x9_adjust_img.png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;prev disabled&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot; bosszone=&quot;rvideo_list_forward&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;next&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot; bosszone=&quot;rvideo_list_back&quot;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol style=&quot;width: 1870px;&quot; class=&quot;rv-playlist-list rv-cf list-paddingleft-2&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a data-vid=&quot;f0019il56vg&quot; data-idx=&quot;0&quot; href=&quot;http://v.qq.com/page/f/v/g/f0019il56vg.html&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot; class=&quot;current&quot; bosszone=&quot;rvideo_list_title&quot;&gt; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;img style=&quot;opacity: 1;&quot; src=&quot;http://vpic.video.qq.com/4202233365/f0019il56vg_ori_1.jpg&quot;/&gt; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;