(2, 'cc', '&lt;p&gt;cc&lt;/p&gt;', 'cc', 0, '', 0, 0),
(3, 'ff', '&lt;p&gt;ffdddd&lt;/p&gt;', 'ff2', 0, '', 0, 0),
(5, 'qq', '&lt;p&gt;qq&lt;/p&gt;', 'qq', 0, '', 0, 0),
(6, '超6省份将上调公务员工资', '&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 0.85em; line-height: 1.8em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;著作权归作者所有。&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;商业转载请联系作者获得授权，非商业转载请注明出处。&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;作者：火晴云&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;链接：https://www.zhihu.com/question/19621333/answer/14509610&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;来源：知乎&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 0.85em; line-height: 1.8em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;#39;Helvetica Neue&amp;#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;似乎大多数回答是一年前的了 &amp;nbsp;更新一下这里的一些争议吧&amp;nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;JQuery从1.7版本开始将bind(),live()和delegate()方法合并成了on()方法了&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;同样unbind(),die()和undelegate()方法也合并成了off()方法&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;新旧API对比:&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;$(&amp;#39;a&amp;#39;).bind(&amp;#39;click&amp;#39;, myHandler);&amp;nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;$(&amp;#39;a&amp;#39;).on(&amp;#39;click&amp;#39;, myHandler);&amp;nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;$(&amp;#39;form&amp;#39;).bind(&amp;#39;submit&amp;#39;, { val: 42 }, fn);&amp;nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;$(&amp;#39;form&amp;#39;).on(&amp;#39;submit&amp;#39;, { val: 42 }, fn);&amp;nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;$(window).unbind(&amp;#39;scroll.myPlugin&amp;#39;);&amp;nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;$(window).off(&amp;#39;scroll.myPlugin&amp;#39;);&amp;nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;$(&amp;#39;.comment&amp;#39;).delegate(&amp;#39;a.add&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;click&amp;#39;, addNew);&amp;nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;$(&amp;#39;.comment&amp;#39;).on(&amp;#39;click&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;a.add&amp;#39;, addNew);&amp;nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;$(&amp;#39;.dialog&amp;#39;).undelegate(&amp;#39;a&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;click.myDlg&amp;#39;);&amp;nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;$(&amp;#39;.dialog&amp;#39;).off(&amp;#39;click.myDlg&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;a&amp;#39;); &amp;nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;$(&amp;#39;a&amp;#39;).live(&amp;#39;click&amp;#39;, fn);&amp;nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;$(document).on(&amp;#39;click&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;a&amp;#39;, fn);&amp;nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;$(&amp;#39;a&amp;#39;).die(&amp;#39;click&amp;#39;);&amp;nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;$(document).off(&amp;#39;click&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;a&amp;#39;);&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;/&gt;了解更多:&lt;span style=&quot;color:#337ab7&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; visibility: hidden; transition: all 0.5s;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;visible&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.5s; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//blog.jquery.com/2011/11/03/jquery-1-7-released/&quot; class=&quot; external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.5s; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;blog.jquery.com/2011/11&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//blog.jquery.com/2011/11/03/jquery-1-7-released/&quot; class=&quot; external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#337ab7&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; visibility: hidden; transition: all 0.5s;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ellipsis&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; transition: all 0.5s;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;transition: all 0.5s;&quot;&gt;&lt;em class=&quot;icon-external&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '叔叔', 0, '', 0, 0);

